409
00:23:54,420 --> 00:23:58,980
[SPEAKER_00] veliki križ je zadesio moju obitelju.

410
00:23:58,980 --> 00:24:01,480
[SPEAKER_00] Zadnje novce,

411
00:24:01,480 --> 00:24:02,500
[SPEAKER_00] još smo se i zadužili,

412
00:24:02,500 --> 00:24:03,859
[SPEAKER_00] uzeli smo auto na kredit,

413
00:24:03,859 --> 00:24:05,519
[SPEAKER_00] dignuli smo kredit

414
00:24:05,519 --> 00:24:06,440
[SPEAKER_00] da kupimo auto

415
00:24:06,440 --> 00:24:10,339
[SPEAKER_00] i netko nam je taj auto ukrao.

416
00:24:10,339 --> 00:24:12,920
[SPEAKER_00] Auto je bio star mjesec dana.

417
00:24:12,920 --> 00:24:15,720
[SPEAKER_00] On ju pita,

418
00:24:15,720 --> 00:24:16,680
[SPEAKER_00] kakav je auto bio?

419
00:24:16,680 --> 00:24:17,619
[SPEAKER_00] Takav i takav.

420
00:24:17,619 --> 00:24:18,940
[SPEAKER_00] A gdje ste živili?

421
00:24:18,940 --> 00:24:19,400
[SPEAKER_00] Tu i tu.

422
00:24:19,400 --> 00:24:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] I on shvati da je on ukrao taj auto.

423
00:24:24,000 --> 00:24:28,859
[SPEAKER_00] Ali kaže,

424
00:24:28,859 --> 00:24:29,720
