426
00:24:30,940 --> 00:24:31,819
[SPEAKER_00] Ona dalje nastavlja,

427
00:24:31,819 --> 00:24:32,359
[SPEAKER_00] ali znaš,

428
00:24:32,359 --> 00:24:35,099
[SPEAKER_00] što god da se dogodilo

429
00:24:35,099 --> 00:24:35,819
[SPEAKER_00] u našoj obitelji.

430
00:24:35,819 --> 00:24:36,579
[SPEAKER_00] Znaš, mi ti uvijek

431
00:24:36,579 --> 00:24:37,539
