433
00:24:38,079 --> 00:24:39,539
[SPEAKER_00] I blagoslovi onoga

434
00:24:39,539 --> 00:24:40,420
[SPEAKER_00] koji nam želi zlo.

435
00:24:40,420 --> 00:24:42,720
[SPEAKER_00] Pa smo tako i molili

436
00:24:42,720 --> 00:24:43,460
[SPEAKER_00] za tog čovjeka.

437
00:24:43,460 --> 00:24:44,460
[SPEAKER_00] Iako nismo znali tkoj,

438
00:24:44,460 --> 00:24:45,359
[SPEAKER_00] mi smo molili za njega,

439
00:24:45,359 --> 00:24:45,619
[SPEAKER_00] Bože,

440
00:24:45,619 --> 00:24:46,400
[SPEAKER_00] blagoslovi ga.

441
00:24:46,400 --> 00:24:47,619
[SPEAKER_00] On ne zna.

442
00:24:47,619 --> 00:24:49,119
[SPEAKER_00] Ko zna kako je odrastao

443
