446
00:24:51,500 --> 00:24:52,119
[SPEAKER_00] bez mame.

447
00:24:52,119 --> 00:24:53,640
[SPEAKER_00] On je jadan.

448
00:24:53,640 --> 00:24:54,440
[SPEAKER_00] Mi imamo sve,

449
00:24:54,440 --> 00:24:54,920
[SPEAKER_00] on je jadan.

450
00:24:54,920 --> 00:24:56,119
[SPEAKER_00] Ajde, tako jer dite rješit ćemo.

451
00:24:56,119 --> 00:24:56,799
[SPEAKER_00] Ali on je jadan.

452
00:24:57,299 --> 00:24:57,839
[SPEAKER_00] slovi ga.

453
00:24:57,839 --> 00:24:59,900
[SPEAKER_00] A on kaže,

454
00:24:59,900 --> 00:25:00,920
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam taj čovjek.

455
00:25:00,920 --> 00:25:05,339
[SPEAKER_00] I rasplaću se

456
00:25:05,339 --> 00:25:05,920
[SPEAKER_00] iza grle.

457
00:25:05,920 --> 00:25:08,200
[SPEAKER_00] I žena kaže,

458
00:25:08,200 --> 00:25:09,519
[SPEAKER_00] sad kad sam te i vidjela,

459
00:25:09,519 --> 00:25:10,900
[SPEAKER_00] ja ti opraštam.

460
00:25:12,900 --> 00:25:14,039
[SPEAKER_00] To je naš Bog.

461
00:25:14,039 --> 00:25:15,720
[SPEAKER_00] Ali to je molitva

462
00:25:15,720 --> 00:25:16,920
[SPEAKER_00] za naše neprijatelje.

463
00:25:16,920 --> 00:25:19,319
[SPEAKER_00] Bog onima koji ga ljube,

464
00:25:19,319 --> 00:25:20,519
[SPEAKER_00] sve okreće na dobro.

465
00:25:20,519 --> 00:25:21,299
[SPEAKER_00] Ali sve.

466
00:25:21,299 --> 00:25:23,640
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam imao

467
00:25:23,640 --> 00:25:24,640
[SPEAKER_00] sabroću i nesreću

468
00:25:24,640 --> 00:25:25,799
[SPEAKER_00] gdje je poginulo dvoje ljudi.

469
00:25:25,799 --> 00:25:27,460
[SPEAKER_00] Gdje sam ubio dvoje ljudi.

470
00:25:27,460 --> 00:25:29,059
[SPEAKER_00] Bog je i to ukrenuo na dobro.

471
00:25:29,059 --> 00:25:30,140
[SPEAKER_00] Jer me je vratio

472
00:25:30,140 --> 00:25:30,859
[SPEAKER_00] na pravi put,

473
00:25:30,859 --> 00:25:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] a i meni je majka

474
00:25:33,000 --> 00:25:33,640
[SPEAKER_00] od tog mladića

475
00:25:33,640 --> 00:25:34,279
[SPEAKER_00] kojeg sam ubio

476
00:25:34,279 --> 00:25:35,180
[SPEAKER_00] oprostila.

477
00:25:35,180 --> 00:25:38,740
[SPEAKER_00] Bog onima koji ga ljube,

478
00:25:38,740 --> 00:25:40,039
[SPEAKER_00] sve okreće na dobro.

479
00:25:40,039 --> 00:25:41,920
[SPEAKER_00] Ali budimo

480
00:25:41,920 --> 00:25:43,079
[SPEAKER_00] u djelatnoj ljubavi,

481
00:25:43,079 --> 00:25:43,980
[SPEAKER_00] ne u pasivnoj.

482
00:25:43,980 --> 00:25:47,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ako ti Bog danas kaže,

483
00:25:47,380 --> 00:25:49,319
[SPEAKER_00] ostani na misi,

484
00:25:49,319 --> 00:25:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] dijete moje,

485
00:25:50,000 --> 00:25:51,779
[SPEAKER_00] dođi pričesti se

486
00:25:51,779 --> 00:25:52,579
[SPEAKER_00] mojim tijelom

487
00:25:52,579 --> 00:25:54,859
[SPEAKER_00] za nekoga tko je daleko,

488
00:25:54,859 --> 00:25:56,579
[SPEAKER_00] učini to

489
00:25:56,579 --> 00:25:58,259
[SPEAKER_00] iz velike ljubavi.

490
00:25:58,259 --> 00:25:59,779
[SPEAKER_00] Zaboravi na trenutak

491
