[SPEAKER_00] svoje potrebe.

492
00:26:00,759 --> 00:26:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] Isus kaže,

493
00:26:02,000 --> 00:26:03,299
[SPEAKER_00] ne blebećite kao pogani,

494
00:26:03,299 --> 00:26:04,119
[SPEAKER_00] mislići da će zbog

495
00:26:04,119 --> 00:26:04,980
[SPEAKER_00] mnoštva riječi

496
00:26:04,980 --> 00:26:05,859
[SPEAKER_00] sad nešto postiđi.

497
00:26:05,859 --> 00:26:07,079
[SPEAKER_00] Ma zna Bog

498
00:26:07,079 --> 00:26:07,779
[SPEAKER_00] što ti treba.

499
00:26:07,779 --> 00:26:09,140
[SPEAKER_00] Pa nije ne otišao na godišnji.

500
00:26:09,140 --> 00:26:10,700
[SPEAKER_00] Nije Bog na godišnji

501
00:26:10,700 --> 00:26:11,980
[SPEAKER_00] kad se tebi nešto dogodilo.

502
00:26:11,980 --> 00:26:13,279
[SPEAKER_00] On zna što ti je.

503
00:26:13,279 --> 00:26:15,099
[SPEAKER_00] Moli za ono

504
00:26:15,099 --> 00:26:16,559
[SPEAKER_00] koje je daleko od njega.

505
00:26:16,559 --> 00:26:17,799
[SPEAKER_00] Jer ti si tu,

506
00:26:17,799 --> 00:26:18,500
[SPEAKER_00] blizu.

507
00:26:18,500 --> 00:26:20,099
[SPEAKER_00] Ako sad umreš

508
00:26:20,099 --> 00:26:22,920
[SPEAKER_00] sa Isusom u srcu,

509
00:26:22,920 --> 00:26:26,160
[SPEAKER_00] možda će neki

510
