518
00:26:34,599 --> 00:26:36,079
[SPEAKER_00] Ma jadni ljudi,

519
00:26:36,079 --> 00:26:37,200
[SPEAKER_00] ej, jadni ljudi,

520
00:26:37,200 --> 00:26:38,579
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam Bogu zahvaljivao

521
