[SPEAKER_00] nisu u tom hodu za smrt.

524
00:26:41,799 --> 00:26:43,319
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim,

525
00:26:43,319 --> 00:26:44,680
[SPEAKER_00] koji se kite duginim bojama,

526
00:26:44,680 --> 00:26:45,839
[SPEAKER_00] ali dugu je Bog stvorio.

527
00:26:45,839 --> 00:26:46,720
[SPEAKER_00] Pa duga je naša.

528
00:26:46,720 --> 00:26:47,640
[SPEAKER_00] Nije duga njihova,

529
00:26:47,640 --> 00:26:48,279
[SPEAKER_00] duga je naša.

530
00:26:48,279 --> 00:26:49,140
[SPEAKER_00] Bog je stvorio.

531
00:26:49,140 --> 00:26:51,259
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam srca zahvaljivao

532
00:26:51,259 --> 00:26:52,759
[SPEAKER_00] što ja nisam među njima.

533
00:26:52,839 --> 00:26:53,579
[SPEAKER_00] A mogo sam bit,

534
00:26:53,579 --> 00:26:53,940
[SPEAKER_00] halo,

535
00:26:53,940 --> 00:26:55,779
[SPEAKER_00] mogo sam bit

536
00:26:55,779 --> 00:26:57,220
[SPEAKER_00] bez iakoj problema

537
00:26:57,220 --> 00:26:58,220
[SPEAKER_00] i bio bi glavni.

538
00:26:58,220 --> 00:27:00,299
[SPEAKER_00] Bio li bi glavni?

539
00:27:00,299 --> 00:27:03,819
[SPEAKER_00] Eto, Bogu hvala na svemu

540
00:27:03,819 --> 00:27:06,019
[SPEAKER_00] i Bog vas blagoslovlja.

541
00:27:22,019 --> 00:27:23,599
[SPEAKER_01] Hvala vam, dragom bratu.

542
00:27:23,599 --> 00:27:24,599
