544
00:27:25,920 --> 00:27:27,400
[SPEAKER_01] Makar sam prošao njegovu knjigu

545
00:27:27,400 --> 00:27:28,299
[SPEAKER_01] Uzuši po prijeku,

546
00:27:28,299 --> 00:27:29,359
